QuestData.Title: Guhruhlruhlruh
QuestData.Description:
The murlocs are usually pretty scared of us, but some bigger one led them into our cavern and they're getting too brave.
Kill their leader. I think its name is something like "Guhruhlruhlruh."
QuestData.CompletionText: Can you pronounce murloc names? I never can.
QuestData.RewardText: That ought to send some of the murlocs packing.
